Tarichi 2.0.1
	=:Feature Added:=
		- Added Skins Chooser.
		- Working Progress status when changing content
		- Submenu level 1 now included inside Top Level Menu
		  * Drag and drop to change Menu Order
		- Pagination for Posts in backpanel
		- Independent Image Uploader
		- comment Management Update 
		  * Select All to Delete / Approval
		  * Comment Moderation Globally
		- Easy to type PHP Syntax for Skins
		- Side Panel items now different between global and read post
		- Using CAPTCHA helper on comment form
		- Tagging for post
		- Add Tag Cloud to Side Panel Item
		- Show By Tag at Frontsite
		- Better Comment Management

	=:Technical Update:=
		- Update to CodeIgniter 2.0
		- Folder based reading for Skin Chooser (./skins/)
		- Descriptions for skin saved on "description.txt"
		- Activating a skin do not require to refresh the whole page
		- Global variable data given for each view ($this->data['variable_name'])
		- All ajax request using Post Method
		- Use global variable for each view file
		- Changing Image Uploader Popup from Dialog to standar :abosulte: div
		- No Direct field_name call in generating template (skins)
		- Change Skins folder structure to /skins/{skin_name}/views/* to protect direct access
		- Type $side_panel only to access side_panel on Skin
		- CAPTCHA images saved on ./captcha folder
		- Two Table added {the_tag : the_tag_id, the_tag_name}, and {the_tag_connector : the_tag_connector_id, the_tag_id, the_post_id}
		- Hide all element using {display:none;} not from javascript

	=:To do List:=
